column5: Anyone been fishing around the Morson Miles bay area?
Caught two 10 pounders last week - was guiding today and caught fish all day long on the reefs .... ran out of minnows.

Guided again today. East wind all day. Fished around North Island, Rubber Island and Pony Island. Caught 100 walleyes (used a clicker to keep track) and only had 4 minnows left over. Biggest fish were 26 and 27 inches.
